copic follow-up, confirming the AGN nature of 44\namong 54 observed sources (81.5\\% of efficiency). From the campaign we\nconcluded that RF2 provides the purest sample of AGN candidates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Apr 2019 18:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-29"}
