o inequalities bounding Betti tables of persistence\nmodules from above and below, via the number of critical cells. Our last result\nis the proof that existing algorithms based on local homotopy expansions allow\nfor efficient computability over simplicial complexes up to dimension $2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2019 09:21:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2021 12:38:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-12"}
