re are at\nleast $24$ patterns of length $5$ that occur with positive upper density. In\nall of the proofs we make extensive use of recent ideas concerning correlations\nof multiplicative functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Apr 2019 10:22:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2019 18:36:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-04"}
